'''Toby Longworth''' is a British actor who worked on [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']]. Longworth voiced two characters for the film: [[Senator]] [[Lott Dod]] (body-doubled by [[Silas Carson]]) and the [[Swokes Swokes]] [[Gorgmonger/Legends|gorgmonger]] [[Gragra]].<ref name="TPM">{{Film|I}}</ref><ref name="TL - SW">{{WebCite|url=https://www.tobylongworth.com/star-wars|text=Toby Longworth - Star Wars|work=[https://www.tobylongworth.com Toby Longworth]|archiveurl=https://archive.vn/jMO7Y}}</ref> Although Senator Dod reappeared in further ''[[Star Wars]]'' media, Toby Longworth was not re-cast.<ref name="Supply Lines">{{TCW|Supply Lines}}</ref><ref name="Queen's Shadow audio">[[Queen's Shadow (audiobook)|''Queen's Shadow'' audiobook]]</ref>

